 *   1. Run the prover and confirm all lemmas verify.
 *   2. Add lemmas for I3 (mutual TEE attestation binding),
 *      I7 (measurement-root binding), and I8 (compliance-capability
 *      downgrade resistance).
 *   3. Document any auxiliary lemmas needed to close the proofs in
 *      reasonable time.
 */
